<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        :root {
            color-scheme: light;
            --bg: #f4efe5;
            --panel: #fffdf8;
            --ink: #1f2937;
            --muted: #6b7280;
            --line: #d6c9b6;
            --accent: #0f766e;
            --accent-strong: #134e4a;
            --error: #b91c1c;
            --success: #166534;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.14), transparent 24rem),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f3ea 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
            color: var(--ink);
        }

        .page {
            width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 32px auto;
            display: grid;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .hero,
        .panel {
            background: rgba(255, 253, 248, 0.92);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.08);
        }

        .hero h1,
        .panel h2 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
        }

        .hero p,
        .panel p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .status {
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .status.success {
            background: rgba(22, 101, 52, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(22, 101, 52, 0.2);
            color: var(--success);
        }

        .status.error {
            background: rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.2);
            color: var(--error);
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            font: inherit;
            background: #fff;
        }

        button {
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            font: inherit;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button.alt {
            background: var(--accent-strong);
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .code {
            margin-top: 14px;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: #f8f5ee;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        .flow {
            padding-left: 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="page">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>JWT Browser Demo</h1>
            <p>Trang nay render bang EJS tren server. Ban bam tung nut de login, goi protected route, refresh token va logout. Moi lan submit, server doc cookie hien tai roi render lai trang de ban nhin ro luong JWT.</p>
            <% if (result) { %>
                <div class="status success"><%= result %></div>
            <% } %>
            <% if (error) { %>
                <div class="status error"><%= error %></div>
            <% } %>
        </section>

        <section class="grid">
            <div class="panel">
                <h2>1. Login</h2>
                <p>Form nay gui username va password len server. Neu dung, server se set 2 cookie la accessToken va refreshToken.</p>
                <form action="/demo/login" method="post">
                    <label for="username">Username</label>
                    <input id="username" name="username" value="<%= username %>" required>
                    <label for="password">Password</label>
                    <input id="password" name="password" value="<%= password %>" required>
                    <button type="submit">Login and set cookies</button>
                </form>
                <div class="actions">
                    <form action="/demo/protected" method="post">
                        <button class="alt" type="submit">Test protected route</button>
                    </form>
                    <form action="/demo/refresh" method="post">
                        <button class="alt" type="submit">Refresh tokens</button>
                    </form>
                    <form action="/demo/logout" method="post">
                        <button class="alt" type="submit">Logout</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel">
                <h2>2. Flow dang dien ra</h2>
                <ol class="flow">
                    <li>Login thanh cong tao access token 15 phut va refresh token 7 ngay.</li>
                    <li>Hai token duoc dat vao cookie httpOnly.</li>
                    <li>Protected route doc accessToken tu cookie roi verify.</li>
                    <li>Refresh route doc refreshToken tu cookie, rotate token cu va set cap token moi.</li>
                    <li>Logout xoa cookie va xoa refresh token khoi bo nho.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid">
            <div class="panel">
                <h2>3. Cookies hien tai</h2>
                <p>Day la gia tri ma server doc duoc tu request cookie. Cookie httpOnly van duoc server nhin thay, du browser JavaScript khong doc truc tiep duoc.</p>
                <div class="code">accessToken:
<%= accessToken || "No accessToken cookie" %>

refreshToken:
<%= refreshToken || "No refreshToken cookie" %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel">
                <h2>4. Payload da decode</h2>
                <p>Phan nay cho thay noi dung payload trong JWT. Day chi la decode de hoc, khong phai xac minh tinh hop le.</p>
                <div class="code">accessToken payload:
<%= JSON.stringify(accessPayload, null, 2) || "null" %>

refreshToken payload:
<%= JSON.stringify(refreshPayload, null, 2) || "null" %></div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
